g.text: 0、下面以一个定时器程序来初步说明EventLoop、Channel和Epoll/Poll(事件描述符)之间的调用关系#include <muduo/net/Channel.h>#include <muduo/net/EventLoop.h>#include <boost/bind.hpp>#include <stdio.h>#include <sys/timerfd.h>using namespace muduo;using namespace muduo::net;EventLoop* g_loop;int timerfd;void timeout(Timestamp receiveTime){printf("Timeout!\n");uint64_t howmany;::read(timerfd, &howmany, sizeof howmany);g_loop->quit();}int main(void){EventLoop loop;g_loop = &loop;timerfd = ::timerfd_create(CLOCK_MONOTONIC, TFD_NONBLOCK | TFD_CLOEXEC);Channel channel(&loop, timerfd);channel.setReadCallback(boost::bind(timeout, _1));channel.enableReading();struct itimerspec howlong;bzero(&howlong, sizeof howlong);howlong.it_value.tv_sec = 1;::timerfd_settime(timerfd, 0, &howlong, NULL);loop.loop();::close(timerfd);//事件循环推出后关闭该文件描述符}

g.text: Channel部分源码解析1(b)一个Channel用于保存一个时间描述符fd的事件及其对应事件发生时的处理函数，Channel的构造函数如下所示：Channel::Channel(EventLoop* loop, int fd__) : loop_(loop), //EventLoop* loop_;用于保存该Channel所属的EventLoop对象 fd_(fd__), //const int fd_; 该Channel负责管理的文件描述符 events_(0), // int events_;用于标记fd需要被监听的事件 revents_(0), // int revents_;用于标记该文件描述符fd已经发生的事件 index_(-1), //int index_; // used by Poller.当前初始化为-1表示没有加入到任何Poller中。详见Poller logHup_(true),//bool logHup_; tied_(false),//bool tied_; eventHandling_(false)//bool eventHandling_;{}Channel中有些事件需要留意： ReadEventCallback readCallback_; EventCallback writeCallback_; EventCallback closeCallback_; EventCallback errorCallback_;这些事件处理函数的赋值函数如下所示： void setReadCallback(const ReadEventCallback& cb) { readCallback_ = cb; } void setWriteCallback(const EventCallback& cb) { writeCallback_ = cb; } void setCloseCallback(const EventCallback& cb) { closeCallback_ = cb; } void setErrorCallback(const EventCallback& cb) { errorCallback_ = cb; }在Channel中用如下常量用于设置fd的监听事件，这和linux中的poll/epoll是一样的： static const int kNoneEvent; static const int kReadEvent; static const int kWriteEvent; const int Channel::kNoneEvent = 0; const int Channel::kReadEvent = POLLIN | POLLPRI; const int Channel::kWriteEvent = POLLOUT;下面这几个函数用于这些事件监听标志的更新，updated定义(e)： bool isNoneEvent() const { return events_ == kNoneEvent; } void enableReading() { events_ |= kReadEvent; update(); } // void disableReading() { events_ &= ~kReadEvent; update(); } void enableWriting() { events_ |= kWriteEvent; update(); } void disableWriting() { events_ &= ~kWriteEvent; update(); } void disableAll() { events_ = kNoneEvent; update(); } bool isWriting() const { return events_ & kWriteEvent; }到这里跳回回到tab(a)

g.text: (e)update()void Channel::update(){ loop_->updateChannel(this);}Channel中的update函数又调用了传入的EventLoop对象的updateChannel()函数，同时将Channel的this指针作为参数传入，该函数定义如下：void EventLoop::updateChannel(Channel* channel){ //判断该Channel是否是属于该EventLoop assert(channel->ownerLoop() == this); //判断该函数是否是在自身EventLoop对象所处线程中被调用 assertInLoopThread(); //调用plller的updateChannel poller_->updateChannel(channel);}channel->ownerLoop()的定义如下：EventLoop* ownerLoop() { return loop_; }直接返回传入该Channel对象的EventLoop指针。assertInLoopThread()函数定义如下： void assertInLoopThread() { if (!isInLoopThread()) { abortNotInLoopThread(); } }其中isInLoopThread()定义如下：bool isInLoopThread() const { return threadId_ == CurrentThread::tid(); }该函数用于判断EventLoop是否处于创建Eventloop对象的线程中，一个EventLoop属于一个线程，而且不能跨线程使用。如果是其他线程调用，那么直接调用：void EventLoop::abortNotInLoopThread(){ LOG_FATAL << "EventLoop::abortNotInLoopThread - EventLoop " << this << " was created in threadId_ = " << threadId_ << ", current thread id = " << CurrentThread::tid();}直接输出错误信息到LOG_FATAL级别日志中，这一级别错误会直接导致程序退出。

g.text: void PollPoller::updateChannel(Channel* channel){ Poller::assertInLoopThread();//调用父类的assertInLoopThread函数 // 打印该channel的文件描述符，打印该channel的fd的监听事件，详见Channel源码2(f) LOG_TRACE << "fd = " << channel->fd() << " events = " << channel->events(); if (channel->index() < 0)//一个Channel如果没有和任何Poller绑定默认初始化为-1,详见Channel源码1(b) {// 一个channel如果没有任何事件需要关注也为负数（见后续分析）。一个Channel第一次和Poller交互会调用这段代码 // a new one, add to pollfds_，确认传入的Channel没有和该Poller关联 // Channels_定义如下，用于保存和该Poller关联的Channel，方便管理Channel // ChannelMap channels_;typedef std::map<int, Channel*> ChannelMap; assert(channels_.find(channel->fd()) == channels_.end()); struct pollfd pfd;//创建一个pollfd结构体 pfd.fd = channel->fd();//将传入的Channel管理的文件描述符赋值给pdf.fd //将传入的Channel管理的文件描述符监听事件赋值给pfd.events pfd.events = static_cast<short>(channel->events()); pfd.revents = 0;//当前该fd没有发生任何事件，pfd.revents赋值为0 // PollFdList pollfds_;typedef std::vector<struct pollfd> PollFdList; // pollfds为int poll(struct pollfd *fds, nfds_t nfds, int timeout);第一个参数用 pollfds.push_back(pfd);//将上述和Channel关联的pfd加入到pollfds_中 //获取当前pollfds_的元素个数，并将该数值作为Channeld的标号(index_的值) int idx = static_cast<int>(pollfds_.size())-1; channel->set_index(idx); //将该channel管理的fd作为key，channel对象作为value插入到channels_中，到这里，一个Channel便和该Poller对象关联 channels_[pfd.fd] = channel; } else// 如果该channel对象之前就加和该Poller关联了，但里面的监听事件改变了则需要更新关联信息 { // update existing one确认传入的Channel已经和该Poller关联了 assert(channels_.find(channel->fd()) != channels_.end()); // 如果传入的Channel已经和该Poller关联了，则继续确认该channel的fd和channel对应，一个fd对于一个Channel assert(channels_[channel->fd()] == channel); int idx = channel->index(); // 再次确认该channel和该Poller关联并存在于pollfds_中 assert(0 <= idx && idx < static_cast<int>(pollfds_.size())); // 更新传入channel在该Poller中的信息 struct pollfd& pfd = pollfds_[idx]; assert(pfd.fd == channel->fd() || pfd.fd == -channel->fd()-1); pfd.events = static_cast<short>(channel->events()); pfd.revents = 0; // 如果传入的channel没有事件需要关注 if (channel->isNoneEvent()) { // ignore this pollfd pfd.fd = -channel->fd()-1; } }}

g.text: // 将传入的channel管理的文件描述符fd添加到epoll中监听，这里和linux的epoll用法完全一样void EPollPoller::update(int operation, Channel* channel){ struct epoll_event event; bzero(&event, sizeof event); event.events = channel->events(); event.data.ptr = channel; int fd = channel->fd(); if (::epoll_ctl(epollfd_, operation, fd, &event) < 0) { if (operation == EPOLL_CTL_DEL) { LOG_SYSERR << "epoll_ctl op=" << operation << " fd=" << fd; } else { LOG_SYSFATAL << "epoll_ctl op=" << operation << " fd=" << fd; } }}

g.text: void EventLoop::loop(){ //保证调用该loop()函数时EventLoop没有处于looping状态，初始化EventLoop时默认是赋值为false assert(!looping_); assertInLoopThread();//确保实在EventLoop所处线程中调用该loop()函数（不可跨线程调用） looping_ = true;//设置EventLoop处于looping状态 quit_ = false;//设置没有退出 //打印该EventLoop地址 LOG_TRACE << "EventLoop " << this << " start looping"; while (!quit_)//条件成立（k） { // ChannelList activeChannels_; // typedef std::vector<Channel*> ChannelList;用于保存有活动的通道 activeChannels_.clear();//清空 // 调用poll函数，传入循环超时时间和activeChannels_， // activeChannels_会在poll返回后拿到有事件发生的channel，poll函数返回本次等待有事件发生的时间戳 pollReturnTime_ = poller_->poll(kPollTimeMs, &activeChannels_); ++iteration_; if (Logger::logLevel() <= Logger::TRACE) { printActiveChannels();//打印活动channel信息 } // TODO sort channel by priority eventHandling_ = true;//设置EventLoop处于“处理事件”状态 // 遍历所有有事件发生的channel，调用对应的事件处理函数根据事件类型(read/write)调用对应的处理函数 for (ChannelList::iterator it = activeChannels_.begin(); it != activeChannels_.end(); ++it) { currentActiveChannel_ = *it; currentActiveChannel_->handleEvent(pollReturnTime_); } currentActiveChannel_ = NULL;//这一轮循环所有事件都处理完了，currentActiveChannel_置空 eventHandling_ = false;//“处理事件”状态为false doPendingFunctors(); } LOG_TRACE << "EventLoop " << this << " stop looping"; looping_ = false;}

g.text: // EPollPoller::poll的道理和PollPoller::poll类似Timestamp EPollPoller::poll(int timeoutMs, ChannelList* activeChannels){ int numEvents = ::epoll_wait(epollfd_, &*events_.begin(), static_cast<int>(events_.size()), timeoutMs); Timestamp now(Timestamp::now()); if (numEvents > 0) { LOG_TRACE << numEvents << " events happended"; fillActiveChannels(numEvents, activeChannels); if (implicit_cast<size_t>(numEvents) == events_.size()) { events_.resize(events_.size()*2); } } else if (numEvents == 0) { LOG_TRACE << " nothing happended"; } else { LOG_SYSERR << "EPollPoller::poll()"; } return now;}

g.text: void EPollPoller::fillActiveChannels(int numEvents, ChannelList* activeChannels) const{ assert(implicit_cast<size_t>(numEvents) <= events_.size()); for (int i = 0; i < numEvents; ++i) { Channel* channel = static_cast<Channel*>(events_[i].data.ptr);#ifndef NDEBUG int fd = channel->fd(); ChannelMap::const_iterator it = channels_.find(fd); assert(it != channels_.end()); assert(it->second == channel);#endif channel->set_revents(events_[i].events); activeChannels->push_back(channel); }}

g.text: void Channel::handleEventWithGuard(Timestamp receiveTime){ eventHandling_ = true; if ((revents_ & POLLHUP) && !(revents_ & POLLIN)) { if (logHup_) { LOG_WARN << "Channel::handle_event() POLLHUP"; } if (closeCallback_) closeCallback_(); } if (revents_ & POLLNVAL) { LOG_WARN << "Channel::handle_event() POLLNVAL"; } if (revents_ & (POLLERR | POLLNVAL)) { if (errorCallback_) errorCallback_(); }//这里的测试代码注册的是timerfd所处channel的读事件，绑定回调函数为timeout(Timestamp receiveTime)，所以该函数会被调用 if (revents_ & (POLLIN | POLLPRI | POLLRDHUP)) { if (readCallback_) readCallback_(receiveTime); } if (revents_ & POLLOUT) { if (writeCallback_) writeCallback_(); } eventHandling_ = false;}
